## Data Flow — Synchronous Batch
```
1. main.py calls AmadeusAdapter.search_flights()
2. AmadeusAdapter returns List[FlightModel] → saved to data/bronze/amadeus/
3. main.py calls DuffelAdapter.search_flights()
4. DuffelAdapter returns List[FlightModel] → saved to data/bronze/duffel/
5. main.py calls FlightValidationService.validate()
6. FlightValidationService returns List[FlightModel] with errors
7. main.py calls FlightScoringService.score()
8. FlightScoringService returns List[FlightModel] with quality_metadata
9. main.py calls FileRepository.save_silver() → data/silver/
10. main.py calls FileRepository.save_gold() → data/gold/
11. main.py calls PostgresRepository.save_results() → dq_results table
```